OL,3,CUnmasked: 'The Gravedigger' who
OL,4,Cbrought members of the Syrian regime
OL,5,Cto justice
OL,7,F'The Gravedigger', a key figure in
OL,8,Fexposing some of the regime's darkest
OL,9,Fcrimes, has now revealed his true
OL,10,Fidentity in an interview with ITV
OL,11,FNews' Global Security Editor, Rohit
OL,12,FKachroo
OL,14,FWhen I ask his name, he gives two
OL,15,Fanswers.
OL,17,F"My real name is Mohammad Afif
OL,18,FNaifeh," he says. Then he pauses and
OL,19,Fquietly adds, "But I'm known as The
OL,20,FGravedigger."
