OL,3,CUnmasked: 'The Gravedigger' who
OL,4,Cbrought members of the Syrian regime
OL,5,Cto justice
OL,7,FFor years, his identity was hidden.
OL,8,FHis face never seen, his voice never
OL,9,Fheard. Yet he became a pivotal figure
OL,10,Fin the pursuit of justice`an anonymous
OL,11,Fwitness to some of the darkest crimes
OL,12,Fof the 21st century.
OL,14,FHis appearance is unremarkable: deep-
OL,15,Fset eyes, long, slicked-back hair.
OL,16,FNothing that would draw a second
OL,17,Fglance on the street.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
