OL,3,CUnmasked: 'The Gravedigger' who
OL,4,Cbrought members of the Syrian regime
OL,5,Cto justice
OL,7,FYet this man has stood before
OL,8,Fparliaments around the world`including
OL,9,Fthe US Congress`and testified in
OL,10,Fcourtrooms in Germany.
OL,12,FHe reaches into his pocket and
OL,13,Fproduces a nylon mask. The moment he
OL,14,Fputs it on, the transformation is
OL,15,Fimmediate.
OL,17,FThis is the face many people across
OL,18,Fthe world came to recognise: the
OL,19,Fmasked witness who helped bring
OL,20,Fmembers of the Syrian regime to
OL,21,Fjustice.
