OL,7,FThe man who exposed its industrial
OL,8,Fscale killing machine. 'The
OL,9,FGravedigger'.
OL,11,F"The worst moment came when the
OL,12,Ftruck's back door opened and the
OL,13,Fcorpses began spilling out," he says,
OL,14,Fas he begins to recall his life
OL,15,Fworking at the mass burial sites.
OL,17,FRefrigerated lorries`sixteen metres
OL,18,Flong`arrived at remote burial sites
OL,19,Fwhere he had been ordered to work.
