OL,5,Cto justice
OL,7,FFor seven years, his role was simple
OL,8,Fand horrifying: bury the dead. Erase
OL,9,Fthe evidence.
OL,11,F"I was in complete shock. I didn't
OL,12,Fknow how to process what I was seeing.
OL,14,F"At first, it was just one or two
OL,15,Fvans`I assumed the bodies were
OL,16,Fsoldiers or accident victims.
OL,18,F"I had no idea those men giving me
OL,19,Forders were from the security
OL,20,Fservices."
