OL,3,CUnmasked: 'The Gravedigger' who
OL,4,Cbrought members of the Syrian regime
OL,5,Cto justice
OL,7,FHe was not a soldier. Not a
OL,8,Fpolitician. He was a low-ranking
OL,9,Fadministrator, handed a shovel and a
OL,10,Fset of orders he could not refuse,
OL,11,Fwho, over time, would bury
OL,12,Fhundreds`perhaps thousands`of victims
OL,13,Fof the Assad regime.
OL,15,F"I had worked for the Public Burial
OL,16,FOffice in Damascus. My job was to
OL,17,Fissue receipts and coordinate
OL,18,Flogistics for families. I had never
OL,19,Fdealt with corpses.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
