OL,5,Cto justice
OL,7,F"Then one day, my manager called me
OL,8,Finto his office. Two men were waiting.
OL,9,FThey told me to go with them."
OL,11,FMohammad was taken to the Najha
OL,12,Fcemetery, just south of the capital.
OL,14,F"I couldn't say no."
OL,16,FThat day, he buried 35 to 40
OL,17,Fbodies`some five to a grave.
OL,19,F"They were wrapped in plastic bags,
OL,20,Fstained with blood. I didn't question
OL,21,Fanything."
