OL,7,FAfterwards, the men told him he was
OL,8,Fdismissed and could return to the
OL,9,Foffice. But two days later, he was
OL,10,Fordered back. And again.
OL,12,FSoon, the vans were replaced by
OL,13,Frefrigerated lorries. The office
OL,14,Fworker who once fainted at the sight
OL,15,Fof blood had been forced into the
OL,16,Fmachinery of mass disposal.
OL,18,FAmong the dead, he began to recognise
OL,19,Fvictims.
