OL,7,F"I found them among the corpses," he
OL,8,Fsays. "Some were friends from
OL,9,Fchildhood.
OL,11,F"Their families had told me they'd
OL,12,Fgone missing in the security branches.
OL,13,FI was shocked to find them there."
OL,15,FHe lowers his voice. "Their families
OL,16,Fhad done everything`paid ransoms,
OL,17,Fbegged for answers`just to know where
OL,18,Ftheir loved ones were.
