OL,7,F"We grew up in the same neighbourhood.
OL,8,FIt wasn't just one friend. There were
OL,9,Fmany."
OL,11,FEventually, he fled Syria. After seven
OL,12,Fyears of digging graves, he escaped
OL,13,Fand was reunited with his wife and
OL,14,Fchildren`far from the sites he had
OL,15,Fbeen forced to serve.
