OL,7,FAfter years as part of the regime's
OL,8,Finfrastructure, he decided to play a
OL,9,Fbigger role in the effort to bring it
OL,10,Fto justice, alongside campaigners from
OL,11,Fthe US-based Syrian Emergency Task
OL,12,FForce.
OL,14,FMohammad spoke out. He made rare
OL,15,Fpublic appearances where he was said
OL,16,Fto be living "somewhere in Europe" or
OL,17,F"at an undisclosed location".
