OL,3,CUnmasked: 'The Gravedigger' who
OL,4,Cbrought members of the Syrian regime
OL,5,Cto justice
OL,7,FNow, the truth can be told: he made
OL,8,Fhis way to Germany after leaving
OL,9,FSyria, using one of the smuggling
OL,10,Fnetworks known to many of his
OL,11,Fcompatriots.
OL,13,FWhenever he appeared before the
OL,14,Fcameras, he wore the mask. He spoke
OL,15,Fonly in hushed tones through an
OL,16,Finterpreter.
OL,18,FIt can now be revealed that he was one
OL,19,Fof several eyewitnesses who helped ITV
OL,20,FNews to identify a mass burial site
OL,21,Fused to dispose of Assad's opponents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
