OL,7,FIn 2023, he helped us to pinpoint the
OL,8,Flocation using satellite images. Now,
OL,9,Ffour months after the collapse of the
OL,10,FAssad regime, he has revealed his
OL,11,Fidentity.
OL,13,FHe still carries the mask with him. He
OL,14,Fknows the risks.
OL,16,F"I've abandoned my mask," he says.
OL,17,F"And now I'm afraid. Assad's people,
OL,18,For their allies`Iran, Hezbollah`they
OL,19,Fcould come for me. Even here in
OL,20,FEurope, I don't feel safe. My family
OL,21,Fdoesn't feel safe."
